into the Village.

17:34.221 --> 17:37.639
They thought it would
scare off the junkies.

17:37.722 --> 17:40.847
It came right into my window
and woke me up.

17:42.221 --> 17:44.639
I was
with a boyfriend.

17:46.305 --> 17:50.180
Anyway, does that
answer your question?

17:50.263 --> 17:52.971
Um, I didn't ask a question.

17:54.013 --> 17:57.221
I'm really sorry about earlier,

17:57.305 --> 18:01.263
